casebody.data:
FIFTH THIRD BANCORP, petitioner,
v.
ARLINGTON VIDEO PRODUCTIONS, INC. No. 13-7. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 515 Fed.Appx. 426 . On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit for further consideration in light of Comcast Corp. v. Behrend, ---U.S. ----, 133 S.Ct. 1426 , 185 L.Ed.2d 515 (2013).
